

GRANT USAGE ON SCHEMA public TO postgres WITH GRANT OPTION;
GRANT USAGE ON SCHEMA mergestat TO postgres WITH GRANT OPTION;
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON ALL TABLES IN SCHEMA public TO postgres WITH GRANT OPTION;
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON ALL TABLES IN SCHEMA mergestat TO postgres WITH GRANT OPTION;
ALTER DEFAULT PRIVILEGES IN SCHEMA public GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON TABLES TO postgres WITH GRANT OPTION;
ALTER DEFAULT PRIVILEGES IN SCHEMA mergestat GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON TABLES TO postgres WITH GRANT OPTION;
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON ALL SEQUENCES IN SCHEMA mergestat TO postgres WITH GRANT OPTION;
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON ALL SEQUENCES IN SCHEMA public TO postgres WITH GRANT OPTION;
ALTER DEFAULT PRIVILEGES IN SCHEMA mergestat GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON SEQUENCES TO postgres WITH GRANT OPTION;
ALTER DEFAULT PRIVILEGES IN SCHEMA public GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON SEQUENCES TO postgres WITH GRANT OPTION;
GRANT readaccess TO postgres;
